    </div>

    <div class="rules">

      <div class="overlay absolute"></div>

      <div class="content-wrapper absolute">

        <div class="exit absolute"><i class="fa red fa-times"></i></div>

        <div class="content">
          <span class="rules-title red bold mb4 h1 ml2">The Rules Of The Game</span>
          <div class="rules-content-wrapper flex-wrap flex flex-justify">

            <!-- Question 1 -->
            <div class="question p2">
              <div class="h4 bold gray2 mb1">How do I play?</div>
              <div class="h4 gray2 mb2">
                <p>It’s simple! Guess how many tomatoes are in the scene and tweet your best guess at @RougeTomateNYC with the tag  #RTChelseaOpening. But - only one guess per person (don’t think we won’t check)! </p>
                <p>The first person to tweet the correct answer wins. If no one tweets the correct answer, the closest guess will take the prize. </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 2 -->
            <div class="question p2">
              <div class="h4 bold gray2 mb1">How do I know if I've won?</div>
              <div class="h4 gray2 mb2">
                <p>We’re monitoring tweets with the hashtag #RTChelseaOpening, so make sure your guess is tagged and we’ll see it! </p> 
                <p>If you win, we’ll Direct Message you on Twitter - so make sure you’re following @RougeTomateNYC</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 3 -->
            <div class="question p2">
              <div class="h4 bold gray2 mb1">What do I win?</div>
              <div class="h4 gray2 mb2">
                <p>The prize this time is dinner & wine for two!</p> 
                <p>Yes - this time. There will be multiple competitions in the coming weeks leading up to the opening, so make sure you revisit this website if you want more chances.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 4 -->
            <div class="question p2">
              <div class="h4 bold gray2 mb1">If I win, when and how do I receive my prize?</div>
              <div class="h4 gray2 mb2">
                <p>Come to Rouge Tomate Chelsea once we open this winter. Prove to us that you’re the user from twitter (show us on your phone) and we’ll get you your winning drinks! </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 5 -->
            <div class="question p2">
              <div class="h4 bold gray2 mb1">I don’t have a Twitter. How do I play?</div>
              <div class="h4 gray2 mb2">
                <p>You can make a Twitter account for free at www.twitter.com!</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 6 -->
            <div class="question p2">
              <div class="h4 bold gray2 mb1">More Questions?</div>
              <div class="h4 gray2 mb2">
                <p>Email or Tweet at us if you have any other questions about the competition.</p>
                <p>E: chelsea@rougetomate.com<br>T: @RougeTomateNYC</p>
              </div>           
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/javascripts/jquery-2.1.4.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/index.js"></script>

